args:
Nefaria unleashes the hidden power of the royal
line upon the imperials, driving them back.
The dunefolk then learn who she is and relay a
message from their ancestors. Feeling the love
of her people well up in her anew, she revels in
their descendants' festival.
You face a choice, dunefolk! Bend the knee\nto the Dyrenell Empire and grant her your\nability, or die screaming on her steel!
They've not sent a force this big before...\nWe'll never be able to hold them off!
...Huh? Hey, what's this surging mana?\nDon't tell me MORE are coming!
Men of Dyrenell, heed this warning!\nI will suffer no further incursion!

Leave the dunefolk in peace forevermore,
or Queen Nefaria shall rend your precious
steel to splinters and ensure none of you
make old bones!
Horus. Nadine. Lend me now your mana.
Very well, Queen of the Sandreach.\nMake manifest your will.
(Ah, their power surges within me...\nThe old magic bubbles to the surface\nof my memory.)
(I'll not repeat my error of yore;\nI shall live on together with those I love!)
Hear your queen, O empyrean blaze!\nHeed me and make manifest your\npurging flames!
Ohmigosh, girl, you did it!\nYou sent that entire army packing!
I know about that spell—it's the birthright\nof the royal line!
But it was lost ages ago. So does that\nmean Ria is actually...?
Aye, my name is Nefaria, final queen of\nthe Sandreach, reborn anew after\ncenturies' slumber.
What is fallen cannot live again: I long\nheld such as natural law unbreakable,\nand no doubt you all held the same.
And my memory remains incomplete,\nmuch of what I knew before lost.

I am flawed now, as in life. Most would
rightly think my claims the height of
madness, and I will not ask that you
believe me.

I mean, I pretty much believed the moment
you showed up with Lord Horus and started
zapping people with ancient magic—but
I'd believe even WITHOUT all that!
We saw you fight on the front lines,\nand you looked every bit the legend!
We have no reason to doubt you.
Yeah, you kinda cranked the queen vibe\nthrough the roof back there, Ria.
I am Nefaria, queen of the Sandreach,\nand I shall live this second life as I did my\nfirst: ever in service of the dunefolk.
Our people aren't asking you\nto stay here with us.
Then pray, why seek me out?\nWas that not the aim of Nadine's travels?
Yeah, I was actually looking for you\nso I could pass on a message—not so\nyou'd have to pack up and move here.
Words passed down through the\ngenerations by our forebears.
They said that if their prayers were ever\nanswered and you came back to life,\nthey wanted you to live it for yourself.
I wanted to bring you here to meet\neverybody so we could tell you that.
I mean, you just woke up and stuff!\nNo one is expecting you to build a\nwhole new kingdom.
That's why we've been traveling—to make\na place for YOU to come home to!
If you came back to life and were all by\nyourself, it'd be lonely—and I KNOW you\nget lonely, so don't even with that.
It's said our queen dedicated her entire\nexistence to the kingdom and its people,\nwhich is why they left those words for you.
They just wanted you to be happy.\nThat's all any of us want.
*sniff* This is fine hearing...\nThank you. Thank you all.
So what's the plan then, girl?
I shall return to the Halidom.
The dunefolk are my beloved people,\nnow as always—but I have found another\nsince awakening that I love no less:
A kind prince who accepted a stranger into\nhis home and urged her find happiness.
I wish to offer what aid and succor to him\nas I can, and see such happiness take root.
Niiice! Okay, then I'm coming too.
But not before we make this\nthe biggest festival yet!
We have to celebrate our queen's\ndeparture on her new journey!
(And to their reborn queen they offer\nfreedom. Is this, too, the work of love?\nOr perhaps...)
Assaying your character will require\nfurther observation, Nefaria.
I shall serve as steward to your memories\nuntil then.
Nice stomping out there, girl! You slayed!
If I was able to bring some joy to the\naudience, I am gladdened by it.
But I feel compelled to ask: You did not\nrecord my image during the show?
Relinquish the device to me at once.
Uh, I mean, noooo! No way, girl!\nI'd never sneak a snap without your say-so!
Then surely showing me the device\nis no cause for disquiet.
Pleeease, Ria, just let me keep one!\nYou look drop-dead GORGE in those!
Indeed, it is quite well taken...
Wait, what? So you're not gonna\nmake me delete it or whatever?
I shall make a rare exception; this image\nwould not exist were I not beloved of my\npeople, now as long ago and longer still.
Well, dur! We love you to bits!
And I thank you for it. ...Er, Nadine?
Whoa, you said it right! Ah, that doesn't\neven matter right now! YES OF COURSE!\nFOREVER AND EVER!
But you KNOW we've gotta get a snap\nto commemorate this mad event!
Oh, are you making one of your pictures\nagain, Nadine? Let us in! Er, do you mind,\nQueen Nefaria?
That idea sounds like the\n＂greatest of all this evening.＂
Oh, eaaasily G.O.A.T.E.! Now c'mon, crew!\nHuddle up while I grab my selfie stick!
